{
  "stem": "21308.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was incredibly efficient and he was very devout, very devout.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he won a military cross in the First World War and we're talking bout the Second World War, so he was no spring chicken.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, I remained very great friends until he died.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And oh, he was a super chap, super chap.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't renamed, it just continued.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They merely changed our form of draft from animal draft to mechanized air-portable.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we're still called-- we were still equipped with the mountain guns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our guns were not the same as the field army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You could take our guns to bits, which was a great asset because you could put them in the landing craft-- little landing craft-- in bits and pieces and then assemble them on the shore where you landed.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it's a big shock to even a German soldier, and the Germans are good soldiers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a shock to him to suddenly find that he had a 3.7 Howitzer firing at him over about 50 yards' range.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By that time-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --by that time, we knew that there was, in fact, an extermination program going on, although it was hotly denied by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, the very fact that they were denying it made us more convinced than ever it was true.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we had no idea that we-- that they-- the program was such as it was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Bear in mind that a British newspaper-- in fact, I've got one in that bookcase but I can't get it out here-- a British newspaper, if it consisted of four sheets, it was a pretty big newspaper then.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The newsprint was very heavily rationed.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
